[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0317","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0317.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0718","title":"IBM GINA for NT 1.0 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"IBM GINA for NT 1.0 存在权限提升漏洞，本地用户可通过修改 GroupMapping 注册表项将自身账户映射到管理员组，从而获取系统管理员权限。该漏洞影响 IBM GINA for Windows NT 系统，需要攻击者已有本地访问权限。攻击者成功利用后可完全控制目标系统，执行任意操作，包括安装程序、修改数据和创建新用户账户。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0718"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2001-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:54.707","remediation":"升级 IBM GINA 到厂商修复版本（1.0 以上版本）；使用注册表编辑器限制 `HKLM\\Software\\IBM\\GINA\\GroupMapping` 键值的写入权限，仅允许管理员组修改；如不再需要 OS/2 域认证功能，建议卸载 IBM GINA 并禁用该组件，或迁移到受支持的认证方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ntbugtraq.com/default.asp?pid=36&sid=1&A2=ind9908&L=ntbugtraq&F=&S=&P=5534","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/608","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3166","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19472"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0317.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0234","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0234.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0681","title":"Microsoft FrontPage Personal Web Server 缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft FrontPage Personal Web Server (PWS) 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送超长 URL 请求触发缓冲区溢出，导致服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows 95 平台上的 FrontPage Server Extensions 3.0.2.926 及可能其他版本，攻击无需身份认证，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0681"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2001-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:50.150","remediation":"立即停止使用 Windows 95 及 Microsoft FrontPage Personal Web Server 1.0，该产品已终止支持且不再有安全更新。建议迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器（如 IIS 或 Apache），并在防火墙层面限制对 PWS 服务的网络访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/1999-q3/0381.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/568","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3117","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19445","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0681.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0681","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0681.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0681.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wj24-pvf2-wxpm/GHSA-wj24-pvf2-wxpm.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/1999.tsv","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_150600_150700.json","https://github.com/CERTCC/SBOM/blob/ae581e32992458f65018df4eced684b7370bba39/SwiftBOM/cpe_lookup/cve_lookup/microsoft/personal_web_server_cve.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0681.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0234.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0234.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0234.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0025","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0025.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0359","title":"Marc Schaefer ptylogin 拒绝服务及密码泄露漏洞","description":"Unix 系统中的 ptylogin 工具存在访问控制缺陷，本地用户可通过操纵伪终端设备锁定调制解调器，导致合法用户无法拨入（拒绝服务）；亦可利用该缺陷以调制解调器身份向外拨号，或截获拨入用户的登录密码。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，影响所有使用 ptylogin 管理串行拨号会话的 Unix 系统，攻击者需具备本地 shell 访问权限即可实施攻击。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0359"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2001-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:13.617","remediation":"立即升级 ptylogin 至最新安全版本；同时移除 ptylogin 二进制文件的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/ptylogin），并将可执行权限限制为仅授权用户组。对调制解调器设备文件（/dev/ttyS*、/dev/modem）设置 600 权限，仅允许 root 和拨号用户组访问。实施回拨认证机制作为临时缓解措施，并建议用 SSH 或 VPN 替代基于调制解调器的远程接入方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0359","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0359.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0359","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0359.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0359.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vwjf-9p53-995f/GHSA-vwjf-9p53-995f.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0359.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82482/info.html","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0025.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0021","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0021.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0307","title":"HP HP-UX cstm 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"HP-UX 操作系统中的 cstm（Customer Services Test Manager）程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向该程序提交特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，进而覆盖内存中的关键数据，实现权限提升并获得 root 超级用户权限。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 多个版本，攻击者需要具有目标系统的本地访问权限，但无需其他特殊条件，利用难度较低，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0307"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2000-12-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:07.113","remediation":"立即移除 cstm 程序的 setuid root 权限位：`chmod u-s /opt/sfm/bin/cstm`，仅允许受信任的管理员通过 sudo 执行。如业务允许，可彻底卸载 cstm 软件包：`swremove SFM-CSTM`。若系统仍在运行关键业务无法直接卸载，应使用文件权限 ACL 限制 cstm 的执行用户为 root 组，命令：`chmod 750 /opt/sfm/bin/cstm && chown root:sys /opt/sfm/bin/cstm`。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0307"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0021.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0477","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0477.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0761","title":"FreeBSD fts 库本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 操作系统的 fts 库例程中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过 periodic 程序触发该漏洞，导致任意文件被篡改。该漏洞源于 fts 库对文件路径名处理时未正确进行边界检查，攻击者利用精心构造的路径名可造成缓冲区溢出，进而修改系统关键文件，影响系统完整性与可用性。CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0761"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-09-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:00.190","remediation":"建议升级 FreeBSD 系统至 3.3 及以上版本，该版本修复了 fts 库例程中的缓冲区溢出问题。对于无法升级的旧系统，可安装 FreeBSD 安全公告提供的对应补丁包。临时缓解措施：限制本地用户对 periodic 程序的执行权限，移除不可信用户的 shell 访问，降低本地提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1074","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/644"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0477.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0576","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0576.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0812","title":"Samba smbmnt 本地文件系统挂载竞争条件漏洞","description":"Samba 组件中的 smbmnt 工具存在竞态条件漏洞，本地攻击者可通过利用文件系统挂载过程中的时间窗口，在任意目录挂载文件系统，导致权限提升或敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Samba 多个版本，需要本地用户权限作为攻击条件，CVSS 评分 7.6，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0812"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-07-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:06.467","remediation":"立即升级 Samba 至 2.0.1 或更高版本，该版本已修复 smbmnt/smbmount 中的条件竞争漏洞。如无法升级，可移除 smbmnt 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/smbmnt），仅允许受信任用户执行，通过文件系统权限限制本地普通用户对 smbmnt 的访问以降低被利用风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0812"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0576.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0172","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0172.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0585","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 与 Windows 2000 默认管理员账户漏洞","description":"Windows NT/2000 系统的内置管理员账户默认名称为 \"Administrator\"，该账户名在系统中为公开已知且无法通过常规方式修改。攻击者可利用这一已知账户名，结合弱口令爆破或字典攻击，远程尝试登录目标系统。由于攻击者无需猜测用户名，仅需破解密码即可获得管理员权限，这显著降低了暴力破解的难度。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 和 Windows 2000 系统，虽然 CVSS 评分较低，但在实际攻击中常被用作信息收集和初始入侵的突破口。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0585"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2000-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:40.933","remediation":"重命名默认 Administrator 账号为其他名称，并创建一个名为 Administrator 但无实际权限的诱饵账户；同时启用账户锁定策略，在 30 分钟内 5 次登录失败后锁定 30 分钟，以防范暴力破解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0585","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0585.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0585","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0585.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0585.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0585.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-w6jm-mv22-w3jr/GHSA-w6jm-mv22-w3jr.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0585.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152600_152700.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--4f1e8558-005f-464b-a513-8b0f99604c5f.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0172.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0300","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0300.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0590","title":"Linux Linux Kernel 未显示用户访问法律警告信息漏洞","description":"Linux 系统在用户登录访问前未显示适当的法律声明或警告信息（如\"仅限授权用户使用\"等提示），导致未经授权的访问者无法获知系统访问权限规定及法律后果。攻击者可在无任何警告提示的情况下直接尝试登录系统，降低了安全策略的合规性。该漏洞影响早期 Linux 内核版本，属于安全策略配置缺陷而非代码逻辑漏洞，通常通过修改 /etc/issue 和 /etc/issue.net 等登录横幅文件添加法律声明来修复。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0590"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2000-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:41.527","remediation":"在 /etc/issue 和 /etc/issue.net 中添加经法务审核的未授权访问警告文本，如 \"WARNING: Unauthorized access is prohibited and subject to legal action.\"。对于 SSH 服务，在 /etc/ssh/sshd_config 中设置 Banner /etc/issue.net 并重启 sshd。对 Telnet/FTP 等服务也需配置对应横幅文件。建议同时设置 /etc/motd 显示登录后法律声明。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/j-043.shtml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0590.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0590","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0590.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0590.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0590.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/b13a5af37e59aa19fd1ac1c09247642e81435453/1999/CVE-1999-0590.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0590.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-05xx/CVE-1999-0590.json","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/cve_info/blob/03b7e36424574a3a9ba5fd13480a326b666a1046/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0590.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0590.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0300.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0855","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0855.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1008","title":"xsoldier 0.96 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"xsoldier 0.96 版本程序在处理命令行参数时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 xsoldier 程序传递超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖返回地址从而劫持程序执行流，成功利用后可获取受影响系统（RedHat 6.2）的 root 权限。该漏洞利用条件为攻击者需拥有本地系统账户，无需其他特殊权限即可实施提权攻击。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1008"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-05-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:30.753","remediation":"升级 xsoldier 至 0.98 及以上版本，或移除 xsoldier 的 setuid 权限位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/xsoldier）以防止本地提权。如无需该游戏，直接通过 rpm -e xsoldier 卸载。建议升级操作系统至受支持的 Red Hat 或 RHEL 发行版。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=freebsd-security&m=94531826621620&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/871","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/229","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1008.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1008","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1008.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1008.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1008.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6ww3-wprw-46qp/GHSA-6ww3-wprw-46qp.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1008.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152300_152400.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0855.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0084","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0084.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0427","title":"Qualcomm Eudora 邮件客户端长文件名附件拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Eudora 4.1 邮件客户端在处理附件文件名时存在缓冲区边界检查缺陷，远程攻击者可通过向目标用户发送包含超长文件名的恶意邮件附件触发此漏洞。当 Eudora 尝试解析或显示过长的文件名时，会导致邮件客户端崩溃或拒绝服务，影响 Eudora 系列产品的正常使用。攻击者无需身份认证即可实施攻击，但需要诱导用户接收并打开邮件。此漏洞 CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0427"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2000-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:22.377","remediation":"升级到 Eudora 4.2 或更高版本，该版本限制附件文件名长度，避免超长文件名导致的拒绝服务。由于 Eudora 已停止维护，建议迁移至 Thunderbird 等现代邮件客户端以持续获得安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0427"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0084.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0295","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0295.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0706","title":"Linux xmonisdn 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Linux xmonisdn 软件包存在本地权限提升漏洞，由于该程序在执行外部命令时未安全处理 IFS（内部字段分隔符）或 PATH 环境变量，本地普通用户可通过修改上述环境变量劫持程序调用的命令执行流程，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞攻击复杂度低，无需用户交互即可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0706"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:53.300","remediation":"建议立即升级 xmonisdn 软件包至厂商修复版本，或删除 xmonisdn 的 setuid 位以消除提权风险。如无需 ISDN 功能，直接卸载 xmonisdn 软件包 (`apt-get remove xmonisdn` 或 `rpm -e xmonisdn`) 作为彻底缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/583"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0295.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0280","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0280.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0701","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 无人值守安装敏感信息泄露漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 在进行无人值守安装后，系统会在本地保留包含敏感配置信息的安装文件（如 Unattended.txt 或 Sysprep.inf），其中可能明文存储本地管理员账户密码。攻击者若能够获取对该文件的读取权限，即可直接提取管理员密码，进而完全控制目标系统。该漏洞源于安装程序未对生成的配置文件设置足够访问限制，属于配置不当问题。CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高，影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统。建议删除安装后残留的配置文件或严格限制其访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0701"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2000-04-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:52.677","remediation":"完成 Windows NT 4.0 无人值守安装后，立即手动删除 %windir%\\system32\\$winnt$.inf 和 $nt4pre$.inf 文件，或使用文本编辑器打开删除其中包含的管理员密码等敏感信息。同时启用 Syskey 工具对 SAM 数据库进行二次加密保护，并限制普通用户对 system32 目录的读取权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ173039","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/626","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-036","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0701.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0701","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0701.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0701.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-26w9-58jr-4jc3/GHSA-26w9-58jr-4jc3.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0701.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ce201f9a-05b7-4813-a26f-ecc530d4b35a.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001276.txt","https://github.com/chandanbn/notes/blob/90eb64532f7259c55e5531dfc2726d810d17ef6e/cve5-validation-errors-Jan27.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0280.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0280.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0525","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0525.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0790","title":"Netscape 浏览器 JavaScript 缓存信息泄露漏洞","description":"Netscape 浏览器存在信息泄露漏洞，远程攻击者可通过构造恶意网页，诱使用户访问后利用 JavaScript 脚本读取浏览器缓存中的敏感信息。该漏洞影响 Netscape Navigator 及 Communicator 系列版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可实施攻击，可能导致用户浏览历史、会话数据等隐私信息泄露。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0790"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:03.810","remediation":"升级至 Netscape 4.5 及以上版本以修复该漏洞；临时缓解措施可在浏览器安全设置中禁用 JavaScript 执行权限。由于 Netscape 浏览器已停止维护，建议迁移至 Mozilla Firefox 等现代浏览器，避免使用已不受支持的旧版浏览器访问互联网。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://home.netscape.com/security/notes/jscachebrowsing.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0525.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0262","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0262.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0693","title":"多厂商 CDE ToolTalk 共享库 TT_SESSION 环境变量缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"ToolTalk 共享库处理 TT_SESSION 环境变量时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可向该环境变量传入超长字符串触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖进程内存空间，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Digital UNIX 4.0、AIX 4.3.2、CDE 2.1、IRIX 6.5.14、Solaris 7.0 及 SunOS 4.1.4 等多个 Unix 系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需具有本地账号方可利用，无需用户交互。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0693"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2000-03-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.690","remediation":"建议安装各厂商当年发布的安全补丁：Sun Solaris 用户安装 Sun Security Bulletin #192 对应补丁(如 107256-xx)；IBM AIX 4.3.2 用户安装 APAR IY07617；HP-UX 用户应用 HPSBUX9909-103 补丁；SGI IRIX 6.5.14 用户安装 SGI 安全补丁；Compaq DIGITAL UNIX 4.0 用户安装对应安全修补包。如无法立即打补丁，可将 ToolTalk 相关二进制文件移除 setuid 权限作为临时缓解措施，或禁用 CDE 环境中的 ToolTalk 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/192","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/641","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9909-103","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A4374","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19501","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0693.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0693","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0693.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0693.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wjxh-cxm3-22mj/GHSA-wjxh-cxm3-22mj.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0693.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152200_152300.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0262.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0173","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0173.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0595","title":"Microsoft Windows NT/2000 页面文件信息泄露漏洞","description":"Windows NT 及 Windows 2000 操作系统在关机时未清除系统页面文件（pagefile.sys）中的残留数据，导致内存中的敏感信息（如明文密码、密钥、用户数据等）可能被写入磁盘并长期保留。本地攻击者在获取系统访问权限后可通过读取页面文件提取这些敏感信息，造成信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及 Windows 2000 系统，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0595"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2000-01-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.143","remediation":"通过本地安全策略启用「关机：清除虚拟内存页面文件」（路径：安全设置→本地策略→安全选项），或设置注册表 HKLM\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\Session Manager\\Memory Management\\ClearPageFileAtShutdown 为 1。建议升级至 Windows 2000 SP4 或更高版本以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/216","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0595.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0595","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0595.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0595.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0595.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-79qg-vhxm-8q4c/GHSA-79qg-vhxm-8q4c.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86259/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://